<title>USA: Schuller completes NRG purchase.</title>
<headline>Schuller completes NRG purchase.</headline>
<dateline>DENVER 1996-08-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Schuller Corp said on Thursday it had completed the acquisition of NRG Barriers Inc for about $72 million in cash, plus existing indebtedness.</p>
<p>NRG is a  manufacturer of polyisocyanurate foam insulation products used primarily in commercial and industrial roofing systems and residential buildings.</p>
<p>NRG is headquartered in Portland, Maine, and has annual sales of about $150 million. The privately held company has about 365 employees.</p>
<p>-- New York newsroom, (212) 859-1610</p>
